{"id":"shapher","term":"Shapher","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Brightness, one of the stations where Israel encamped in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:23\">Num. 33:23</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:24\">24</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:23","Numbers 33:24"]}